Drishyam AI’s Image Recognition technology can be embedded or integrated into your company’s app. Contact us to see how you can decrease customer support costs, improve customer experience, and increase profit margins.

Plumbers spend their day trying to identify and locate the parts they need to fix their clients' faucets. With our image recognition, they can easily identify the exact part they need with ease, allowing them to spend less time on each job and serve more clients each day.

Our image recognition uses the exact contours of a faucet to identify the exact make and model. This can decrease if not eliminate calls to customer support, reducing your customer support costs #KBTribeChat

Product identification is time-consuming, error-prone, and frustrating. Image recognition can reduce customer support costs. Customers snap a photo of the product, and our software instantly identifies the make and model. Faster answers for them, cost savings for you!

Faucet wholesalers spend endless amounts of time searching for faucet parts. With our image recognition technology, wholesalers can search for parts more quickly and efficiently, allowing them to serve more customers each day.

Image recognition can help manufacturers cut down on customer support costs. Customers can use image recognition to find out the make and model of their faucet or part, dramatically reducing the call time with customer support, if not eliminating the call completely.

Using our What's My Faucet! app, plumbers can easily identify the exact make and model of a faucet, as well as individual parts of the faucet. This will reduce the time spent with each client, and, in turn, it will allow them to serve more clients each day.

Using our What's My Faucet! app, image recognition can capture the specific contours of this faucet and identify the exact make and model. Check out this example of image recognition using a Moen faucet. Visit http:// drishyam.ai to learn more. pic.twitter.com/aVBNFNR2kp

Using our image recognition technology, our App can identify the exact make and model of this faucet. This will shorten the time customer support employees spend on the phones with a customer, allowing them to assist more customers each day.
